<p>Founded by the Ukraine Colonist Alliance, the construction of Taras Shevchenko Hub was delayed by almost a month due to paperwork going missing at the Council. The delay, however, did allow the procurement of additional equipment, and the Hub still has a considerably better shipyard and outfitter than comparable surface ports.</p>
<p>The refineries of Mriya focus on non-metallic produce supporting Colonia's military forces, with Explosives and Military Grade Fabrics being produced in large quantities. The UCA's experience with refining was extended into running the nearby Luchtaine facilities in July 3303.</p>
